text: While I haven't played this futuristic racing series as much as F-Zero or even the Extreme-G games on the N64, I've had some good times with it. Wipeout Pure and Pulse are probably the ones I played the most because I liked their portability. Music like this fits the fast paced racing very well. RIP SCE Studio Liverpool, a very unfortunate move by Sony.
